author: Yetti Tri Wulandari
text:
My advices to anyone who deal with insomnia instead of taking sleeping pills :
1. Read books
2. Stay away from your phone
3. Drink one glass of water before bed 
4. If you have an air cond in your room, make it as cool as possible 
5. Thick blanket needed

100% works, I guarantee
